# Naming Conventions

## Endpoints
- All endpoint paths are kebab-case: `/predict-single`, `/predict-batch`, `/model-info`.
- All routes are prefixed with `/api/v1/`.
- Router file: `src/routes.py` or `src/api/v1/routes.py`.

## Pydantic Models
- Suffixed by purpose: `PredictionRequest`, `PredictionResponse`, `HealthResponse`.
- Never use raw dicts for request/response bodies.

## Model Artifacts
- File naming: `{model_type}_{dataset}_{YYYYMMDD}.joblib`
- Example: `random_forest_iris_20250224.joblib`
